34:16.626 --> 34:18.416
It's not a thing. It's just...

34:19.751 --> 34:21.960
You just get it. It's a...

34:22.376 --> 34:23.666
Oh, it's a way of, um...

34:24.417 --> 34:27.956
it's a way of figuring things out
without having to think too hard or...

34:28.458 --> 34:30.458
or talk, more importantly.

34:32.167 --> 34:35.877
You know, most people who die in
the bush... they're found naked.

34:36.292 --> 34:37.132
Ew.

34:37.132 --> 34:40.456
