38:51.792 --> 38:53.382
Did he push you
in those prickles?

38:53.459 --> 38:56.128
Yeah, probably. Did he push
you in the prickles, mate?

38:56.129 --> 38:57.166
Leave him alone.

38:57.209 --> 38:58.829
You shut your trap, old fulla.

38:59.917 --> 39:02.747
